Category "Smoke", Category "Regression"
View->Terminal
To run in command -cd CSharpSelFramework - To run all tests
dotnet test CSharpSelFramework.csproj --filter TestCategory=Smoke - To run by category
In the program put this
string browserName;
browserName=TestContext.Parameters["browserName"];
if(browserName==null)
{
browserName=ConfigurationManager.AppSettings["browser"];
}
dotnet test CSharpSelFramework.csproj --filter TestCategory=Smoke --TestRunParameters.Parameter\(name=\"browserName\",Value=\"Chrome\"\)



